title: Harry Potter and the Deathly Hallows Audio Book
description:
Book 7. Harry Potter & the Deathly Hallows

Organized

Perfect Quality (160KBPS)

Ripped from CDs

Read by Jim Dale

Seed....

Enjoy this one, it is sad to think that harry potter is all over, and i just REALLY got into it not even a year ago. I am so mad at myself. I would have loved to be the one standing in line for hours on end to get one of the books. 
Not to mention the movies.
BY the way...who else is angry that they delayed the Half-Blood PRince by nine months????
That was a sad day for me.
